| (3.1.2.a) |  | \displaystyle\begin{split}f^{!}:\mathscr{L}(X)&\to\mathscr{L}(Y)\\ v&\mapsto f^{\*}v\otimes\omega\_{f}.\end{split} | |  |

We obtain an extension of the previous pseudo-functor

